2. If I keep within the Pounds 3,250 limit, need I declare this income on my
annual tax return?
1. No (so far as we can deduce from the facts given). Ask your tax office
for the free pamphlets CGT4 (Owner-occupied houses) and IR87 (Rooms to let).
2. Yes.
