<DATELINE>
   ZURICH
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Saurer, the Swiss textile machinery and motor components group, said its net
profit last year was higher than the SFr21.4m (Dollars 14.4m) earned in 1992
when operating profit was flat at SFr54.5m.
In a preliminary statement, the group described the result, on sales off 5.6
