Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Atkins Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2251 Women's Hosiery, Ex Socks.
    P2252 Hosiery, NEC.
