the name Akuma, which means 'devil'. The justice ministry was unhappy with
this moniker and, after a seven-month tussle, Shigeharu Sato, the hitherto
stubborn father, has given in. He is following his wife's suggestion. She
has plumped for Jin, which means 'God'.
